member.name: M:ASP.Claims.API.API.Validators.VehicleClaimDtoValidator.ABC123Regex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^[A-Za-z]{3}\\d{3}$
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match a character in the set [A-Za-z] exactly 3 times.
○ Match a Unicode digit exactly 3 times.
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.

member.name: M:ASP.Claims.API.API.Validators.VehicleClaimDtoValidator.ABC12DRegex
member.remarks:
Pattern:
^[A-Za-z]{3}\\d{2}[A-Za-z]{1}$
Explanation:
○ Match if at the beginning of the string.
○ Match a character in the set [A-Za-z] exactly 3 times.
○ Match a Unicode digit exactly 2 times.
○ Match a character in the set [A-Za-z].
○ Match if at the end of the string or if before an ending newline.
